headline: 3 Growth Stocks Trading Near Their 52-Week Lows to Buy Right Now
summary: There are plenty of growth stocks trading at obscenely high valuations right now.  If you're on the hunt for some deals and are willing to be patient, three overlooked stocks you should consider loading up on right now are AstraZeneca (NASDAQ: AZN), United Parcel Service (NYSE: UPS), and Dollar Tree (NASDAQ: DLTR).  Shares of AstraZeneca finished last week just a few dollars away from the stock's 52-week low of $60.47.
